capital one 
-Location Analysis
	-importance with every day life, etc. finding a new house, cirme, schools, etc.
	-can be used to allocate limited resources
	-Identifying possible store locations. Find places where people dont have to walk far or where they will already be congregating from far places at like shopping centers
	-Gravity Model use to determine which possible store locations would be most attractive to the potential/target customer
	-piggybacking off of established stores which attract the desired clientelle. Renting real estate instead of buying so they can easily pack up and move if things go south.